  "macro_plan": "Nykthos Ramp is a Mono-Green deck that leverages Devotion to Green and massive mana acceleration to flood the board with creatures quickly. Though it lost its previous combo-focused identity after Karn, the Great Creator was banned, it now functions as a consistent ramp-combo hybrid that aims to win on explosive turns. The deck relies on a core engine of Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx, dorks, and board-fillers to overwhelm opponents before they can stabilize.",
